name: Crypto Dealer's Story II - 2nd Negative - Statue of Liberty
description: How many memories come to my mind when I see this photo... That's when I saw the Statue of Liberty for the first time. She was smoking a joint much bigger than mine. I felt envy, but at the same time a desire for a challenge, and decided to make a joint of her size. Liberty and I smoked that joint and enjoyed a sunset. Christ, the Redeemer, arrived later from Rio de Janeiro and decided to spend vacations with us. We lived in a beautiful love triangle for 6 long months, but, as expected, as I was not a statue, I ended up, little by little, being excluded. Anyway, those were the most torrid months of my life. We live on marijuana, champagne, chocolate and sex, lots of sex...
